Parliament, Wednesday, 13 March 2019 – The Ad Hoc Committee to Amend Section 25 of the Constitution will today consider a draft report of its work. Details are as follows: 
	
	Date: Wednesday, 13 March 2019
	Time: 13:00 pm
	Venue: Committee Room G26, Ground Floor, National Assembly Building. ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE AD HOC COMMITTEE TO AMEND SECTION 25 OF THE CONSTITUTION, MS THOKO DIDIZA. For media enquiries or interviews, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
	Tel: 021 403 8437
	Cell: 081 703 9542
